theorem closure_interior_closure_eq_closure_of_open {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} (hA : IsOpen A) :
    closure (interior (closure A)) = closure A := by
  apply subset_antisymm
  ·
    have hsubset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
    exact closure_mono hsubset
  ·
    have hA_sub : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure A) :=
      interior_maximal (subset_closure : (A : Set X) ⊆ closure A) hA
    have hclosure : closure A ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) :=
      closure_mono hA_sub
    exact hclosure

theorem closure_interior_closure_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
  exact closure_mono (interior_subset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A)

theorem closure_interior_mono {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hAB : (A : Set X) ⊆ B) :
    closure (interior A) ⊆ closure (interior B) := by
  exact closure_mono (interior_mono hAB)
